The paper deals with the problem of robot coordination, which is a common topic in the fields of multi-agent systems (cs.MA) and robotics (cs.RO). The dispersion problem is a graph problem, which falls under the category of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) and distributed computing (cs.DC). The paper also discusses the use of communication among robots, which is a topic in social and information networks (cs.SI).
